<p><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>On the Picket Line</b></font></p>
<p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">July 6, 2001 | Pages 14 and 15</font></p>

<p><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3">OTHER STORIES BELOW<br>
<a href="#Washington">Washington state workers</a><br>
<a href="#Wisconsin">Wisconsin state workers</a><br>
